>>> Surf_Greatriver_Xtreme_v4 <<<

This is a another surf_greatriver version. 
Many tricks and secruits make this map for the best.

Our Website : www.X-Stylez.de

Changes made from -> xtreme ->> xtreme_v2 ->>> xtreme_v3 ->>>> xtreme_v4

- A lot of optimization, bugfixes
- Reduced filesize
- Texture change
- Delete the teleporter on pool
- Anti-camp on super-sky
- Anti-AFK on spawn
- Added a Adminroom
- Added 1 bigger secret -> Blue lasers in jail
- Added 2 Secruits on jail when the Lasers are on.
- Delete the "Knife room"
- Another Bridge
- Replaced lettering with new
- Edit the water on super-top
- Added surfs on top
- Delete surf on supersky
- Direct access to boost beneath pool
- Added a few secret teleports
- Edit the Weapon platform
- Added a AFK platform
- Added Surf on the pool
- Spritetrail Weapons in the adminroom
- Monitor on the jail-teleport
- Many logos have been added to information over us.
- Custom textures

->>> And more on the Xtreme-Map , have fun
